@node History "SoundDT v41.8 - History of Changes"

v41.0
   Àáfirst public release.

v41.1
   À implemented ahi support.
   À supports 16bit samples now.
   À STM_STOP crashed.
   À a doubleclick on the image will stop the sound now.
   À always tries to allocate two stereo channels, on failure
     a stereo sample will be played on a single channel.
   À now aborts a playing sound and restarts it when the image is pressed
     while playing.
   À developer information are now available
   À the waveform image is now drawn faster and doesn't requiere any memory
     for rendering.
   À some changes I can't remember ;)

v41.2
   À finally, MAUD.datatype (and older versions of aiffdt) work.
   À now it's possible to mark a part of the sample in order to save it to
     the clipboard (DTM_SELECT).
   À disabled panning for stereo samples.
   À new option FAM=FORCEAHIMODE/S.

v41.3
   À fixed some small bugs (nothing serious).
   À works with protracker.datatype now.
   À fixed display problem when using sounddt in conjuction with 
     embed.datatype.
   À added some security checks and semaphore protection.
   À optionally displays a control panel now.
   À two new prefs options (BUFFERSIZE,CONTROLPANEL).

v41.4 INTERNAL RELEASE (due to aminet related problems;)
   À implemented SDTA_Continuous (now works correctly with animation.datatype).
   À fixed a bug of the AHI player routine where a pointer wasn't correctly
     intialized.
   À new option AHIMIXFREQ.
   À again fixed some small bugs.
   À tracked down and fixed a bug that were produced by the compiler and 
     caused a lot of enforcer hits (MaxonC compiled the program correctly, 
     GNUC didn't [public releases are compiled with GNUC]).
   À prefs system didn't work correctly.

v41.5
   À waveform drawing routine didn't draw the 2nd channel of 16bit samples
     correctly.
   À 16sv stereo saving routine produced trash.
   À implemented DTM_DRAW.
   À updated developer docs a bit.
   À volume slider looks like a gadtools one now (can be turned off by 
     NOGTSLIDER).

v41.6
   À updated revision number (41.5 wasn't v41.5 but v41.4 ;)
   À saving of IFF files (DTWM_IFF) crashed, funny that I didn't recognize 
     that before (GMultiview 'Project/Save as IFF ...').

v41.7
   À some small changes.
   À added some macros to the .h file.
   À the v41.7 release actually replaces the "update" archives available.

v41.8
   À implemented DTA_Repeat and DTA_Immediate (GMultiview IMMEDIATE, REPEAT).
   À fixed bug of audio.device player (samples weren't correctly repeated).
   À changed volume slider to make it work properly with VisualPrefs.
   À fixed and optimized library module.
   À added workaround for a bug (?) of gmultiview 45.8, after changing the
     objects' DTA_ControlPanel attribute, GM_LAYOUT (AddDTObject) is called
     but not GM_RENDER (RefreshDTObject should follow AddDTObject).
   À drawing pens are allocated during GM_LAYOUT now and released at 
     DTM_REMOVEDTOBJECT. This avoids "color changes" when a "MagicMenu" popup.

@endnode
